%% ActivaClub - Registration + Email Verification Flow (AC-001 / AC-002 / AC-003 / AC-004)
%% Diagram 2 of 8
%% Last updated: 2026-04-05

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant MembersLambda
    participant SeedDB as DynamoDB (SeedMembersTable)
    participant MembersDB as DynamoDB (MembersTable)
    participant Cognito
    participant CES as CustomEmailSender Lambda
    participant KMS as AWS KMS
    participant SES as Amazon SES

    Note over User,Cognito: STEP 1 — Registration (POST /v1/auth/register)

    User->>Frontend: Fill DNI, email, password on /register
    Frontend->>MembersLambda: POST /v1/auth/register { dni, email, password }
    MembersLambda->>SeedDB: GetItem { pk: "DNI#<dni>" }
    alt DNI not found
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 404 DNI_NOT_FOUND
    end
    alt account_status == inactive
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 403 ACCOUNT_INACTIVE
    end
    MembersLambda->>MembersDB: Query GSI_DNI + GSI_Email (duplicate check)
    alt Already registered
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 409 DNI_ALREADY_REGISTERED / EMAIL_ALREADY_IN_USE
    end
    MembersLambda->>Cognito: SignUp { email, password, custom:dni }
    Cognito->>CES: Trigger CustomEmailSender { code (KMS-encrypted), email }
    CES->>KMS: Decrypt code
    KMS-->>CES: Plaintext 6-digit OTP
    CES->>SES: SendEmail { to: email, body: OTP code }
    SES->>User: Email with 6-digit OTP (TTL 24h)
    MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 202 — Code sent to email

    Note over User,Cognito: STEP 2 — Email Verification (POST /v1/auth/verify-email)

    User->>Frontend: Enter 6-digit OTP on /verify-email
    Frontend->>MembersLambda: POST /v1/auth/verify-email { email, code }
    MembersLambda->>Cognito: ConfirmSignUp { email, code }
    alt Code invalid / expired
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 400 INVALID_CODE / 410 CODE_EXPIRED
    end
    Cognito-->>MembersLambda: User status CONFIRMED
    MembersLambda->>Cognito: AdminGetUser (read custom:dni + sub)
    MembersLambda->>SeedDB: GetItem (get membership_type)
    MembersLambda->>Cognito: AdminAddUserToGroup { GroupName: "Member" }
    MembersLambda->>MembersDB: PutItem { MEMBER#<ulid>, PROFILE, all fields }
    MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 201 — Account activated
    Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /login

    Note over User,Cognito: OPTIONAL — Resend Code (POST /v1/auth/resend-code)

    User->>Frontend: Click "Reenviar código" on /verify-email
    Frontend->>MembersLambda: POST /v1/auth/resend-code { email }
    MembersLambda->>Cognito: ResendConfirmationCode { email }
    Cognito->>CES: Trigger CustomEmailSender (new OTP)
    CES->>SES: SendEmail (new code)
    SES->>User: New 6-digit OTP email
    MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 200 — Code resent
